title: Saga: Rage of the Vikings OST, game soundtrack, Roberto Basarte
description:
This is the cool soundtrack from oldschool rts game - Sage: Rage of the Vikings. (1998). Soundtrack was composed by Roberto Basarte, and after all this years I still listen in. Beacause of that i want to shar this beauty music with You. :)
